Super Eagles coach Gernot Rohr mark his birthday today  the twenty – eighth day of June, National Daily learnt.


The players sang a happy birthday song  to the Franco German coach because the commencement of the evening training in Alexandria, Egypt.

John Ogu led the players in the birthday song. Players like Kenneth Omeruo, Ahmed Musa and Shehu Abdullahi amongst others showered the coach with encomiums on the occasion of his birthday.

Here’s wishing the Super Eagles coach many happy returns of the day.

			
